.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
City: edinburgh, new-york, boston, paris
4 different pets are kept: snake, goat, lizard, goldfish
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person traveling to paris is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is the owner of the snake##1
5. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to new-york##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| City   | new-york     | boston           | edinburgh | paris  |
| Pet         | snake | goldfish | goat   | lizard |

