.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, turquise, lilac, blood-red
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, davidoff, pall-mall, bongani
1. the person who likes turquise is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person who likes mauve is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who likes lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | blood-red   | turquise | mauve | lilac      |
| Cigar     | pall-mall | baccarat    | davidoff  | bongani |

