.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, fanta, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, r&b, disco, soul
1. the fan reggae is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the fan r&b is between the person drinking fanta and the fan disco##2
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
4. the fan reggae is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage       | tea | 7up | fanta     | sprite   |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | r&b     | soul | reggae |

