.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, tiparillo, chaman, fonseca
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, family, horror, comedy
1. the chaman-smoker is between the person watching satire movies and the siglo-smoker##2
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | chaman | siglo | fonseca |
| Movie-Genre   | satire         | comedy       | family    | horror         |

