.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, december, april
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts, spy, satire
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person watching satire movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Birthday    | april   | december      | february   | january  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | martial-arts | spy | superhero |

