.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, october, april
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, tea, fanta
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday          | january     | november | april   | october        |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea   | juice | fanta |

