.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, cat, ferret
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, pink, aquamarine, orange
1. the person who likes aquamarine is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes grey is the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the cat is the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the person who likes pink is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Pet         | hedgehog | cat | ferret | hamster |
| Color   | aquamarine          | pink     | orange  | grey     |

