2. the prince-smoker is between the townhouse house and the fonseca-smoker##2
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
4. the wooden house is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar         | fonseca      | prince | bongani  | baccarat |
| House   | wooden | tower  | townhouse | modern    |

