.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, cauliflower, kale, cranberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, filmmaking, dancing, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person eating cranberry is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person eating kale is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person eating cauliflower##2
4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating kale##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Food   | cucumber | cauliflower | kale | cranberry |
| Hobby     | video-games     | filmmaking   | gardening | dancing  |

