2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to prague and the person who's birthday is in november##2
4. the person traveling to miami is the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | august | november | march | february |
| City           | new-york  | miami  | edinburgh | prague      |

