3. the wooden house is between the person watching sports movies and the modern house##2
4. the art-deco house is the person watching sports movies##1
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| House       | art-deco | wooden | modern | futuristic |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | spy  | comedy    | scientific       |

