.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, bellflower, poppy
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person drinking water is the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who growspoppy is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking sprite##2
5. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | water   | juice   | mirinda | sprite |
| Flower         | azalea | dahlia | poppy     | bellflower    |

