.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, parkour, golf, soccer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, rock, d&b, pop
1. the fan rock is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is between the fan punk and the person who's sport is soccer##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Sport   | golf    | soccer     | basketball | parkour |
| Music-Genre     | rock | pop | d&b       | punk     |

 